parameters: \nc<>Yes, I'm alive. I lost that day, but...

\nc<>Ah, no. Today's stream is not about defeating villains. As
for what I've been doing until now... um...

\nc<>Levantia-san, I understand that you're happy to meet the
listeners after a long time, but please get to the main
point quickly.
\nc<>I don't want to divert the conversation.

\nc<>What's with that expression? Do you want to be educated
again?

\nc<>Ku... I-I understand... From now on, I'll... do it
properly...

\nc<>I, magical girl Levantia... was defeated by Mr. Hypnosis
and captured by the minions of the Paradise Cult--

\nc<>That's not it, right? Can't you even properly say your own
position?
\nc<>I... became a tool for sexual processing.

\nc<>In addition, today through my channel, I would like to
convey the full details of the Paradise Cult to everyone.

\nc<>Hmmm, the last word was unnecessary, but oh well. By the
way, this is quite an impressive graffiti.

\nc<>Ku...! Did you draw this without permission!? I'm not a
perverted woman who would do something so vulgar...!
\nc<>This is the kind of place it is.

\nc<>So, after watching this video, I kindly ask all of the
listeners to make the right judgment without being swayed by
desires.
\nc<>[The event will proceed to the next stage. Are you sure?]

\nc<>What's wrong, Levantia-san? Are there still facilities left
in the school?

\nc<>Ku...! I can't stand this fake religious propaganda
anymore! I can't take it any longer!

\nc<>If you didn't have that stupid hypnotic or whatever
power...! Is it fun to manipulate people without their
consent!?

\nc<>Oh, well, when you say that, it hurts my heart. I am
sincerely working for the happiness of others, you know.

\nc<>There's no helping it, huh? This time, as a special favor,
I will release the hypnosis that was cast on you.
\nc<>Huh...? Is this some kind of trap?

\nc<>There's no trap or anything. I wouldn't want to be
misunderstood by the listeners.
\nc<>How is it? Has the hypnosis been properly lifted?

\nc<>The leader is such a jokester! Using my past self for the
promotion of the Paradise Religion is going too far!
\nc<>I thought it would be more effective, not as a joke...

\nc<>Ahem. Well, now that it's come to this, there's no choice
but to start over.

\nc<>Yes! I am Levantia, the sex processing meat toilet slave of
the Paradise Religion!

\nc<>My special skill is giving blowjobs, and I love being used
roughly like a tool

\nc<>Ah, you properly did the graffiti that I asked for. It
really gives off the feeling of being a meat toilet when
there's stuff like this!
\nc<>It might have been a mistake to undo the hypnosis...
\nc<>[The event will proceed to the next stage. Are you sure?]
